emperature of\n5625 K for the stellar photosphere, the spots temperature ranges mainly from\n3600 to 5000 K. The results from the spot modeling are in agreement with those\nfound for magnetic activity analysis from out of transit data of the same star.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Tue, 22 Sep 2009 17:57:24 GMT"}],"update_date":"2015-05-14"}
