ing an alternative scenario that emerges naturally from\ncosmological simulations.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Tue, 22 Sep 2009 20:03:54 GMT"},{"version":"v2","created":"Thu, 13 May 2010 20:58:47 GMT"}],"update_date":"2015-05-14"}
